## Capacitor 完整起步

### 安裝
```bash
npm install @capacitor/core @capacitor/cli
npx cap init "AI 島" "tw.snowrealm.aiisland"
```

### 加平台
```bash
npx cap add ios
npx cap add android
```

### Build flow
```bash
# 1. Web 先 build
npm run build

# 2. 同步到原生
npx cap sync

# 3. 開原生 IDE
npx cap open ios     # → Xcode
npx cap open android # → Android Studio
```

## 用原生 API

### Camera
```bash
npm install @capacitor/camera
npx cap sync
```

```javascript
import { Camera, CameraResultType } from "@capacitor/camera";

const photo = await Camera.getPhoto({
  resultType: CameraResultType.Uri,
  quality: 90,
  source: CameraSource.Camera
});

img.src = photo.webPath;
```

### Geolocation
```javascript
import { Geolocation } from "@capacitor/geolocation";

const pos = await Geolocation.getCurrentPosition();
console.log(pos.coords);
```

### Filesystem
```javascript
import { Filesystem, Directory } from "@capacitor/filesystem";

await Filesystem.writeFile({
  path: "data.json",
  data: JSON.stringify({ ... }),
  directory: Directory.Data
});
```

### Local Notifications
```javascript
import { LocalNotifications } from "@capacitor/local-notifications";

await LocalNotifications.schedule({
  notifications: [{
    title: "今日提醒",
    body: "繼續學 Ch 5！",
    id: 1,
    schedule: { at: new Date(Date.now() + 60_000) }
  }]
});
```

### Storage（取代 localStorage）
```javascript
import { Preferences } from "@capacitor/preferences";

await Preferences.set({ key: "user", value: JSON.stringify(user) });
const { value } = await Preferences.get({ key: "user" });
```

## Web vs Native fallback
```javascript
import { Capacitor } from "@capacitor/core";

if (Capacitor.isNativePlatform()) {
  // 用原生 API
  await Camera.getPhoto(...);
} else {
  // Web fallback
  document.querySelector('input[type="file"]').click();
}
```

## Live Reload（開發超方便）
```bash
npx cap run ios --livereload --external
npx cap run android --livereload --external
```
改 web、原生 App 自動 hot reload。

## 上架

### iOS App Store
- Apple Developer $99/年
- Xcode build + Archive
- TestFlight 內測
- App Store Connect 上架

### Google Play Store
- Google Play Developer $25 一次
- Android Studio Build AAB
- Play Console 上架

## 心法
- 90% code 共用 web
- 平台特定用 if Capacitor.isNativePlatform()
- Live reload 加速開發
- 上架 Apple > Google（嚴格但 user 多）

**☕ 用人話講**

Capacitor 進階整合：把 PWA 變原生 App，用它**存取 iOS / Android 的原生功能**（相機、檔案、推播）。**一句話記住**：像給網頁 App 裝「原生外掛」——當你需要相機、藍牙、檔案系統這些手機功能時，Capacitor 幫你把網頁跟原生能力接起來。

